content:
Many Chat features are available in both Salesforce Classic and Lightning Experience. Continue customizing your Chat implementation by setting up:

Create Automated Chat Invitations that appear as animated pop-ups on your website to invite customers to chat with an agent.

Create Quick Text Messages to insert into emails, chats, tasks, events, and more.

Add Terms and Conditions Acceptance to your Pre-Chat Form to inform customers about conversation data tracking or sharing other information.

Set Privacy Options for Chat Users to block sensitive data and unwanted visitors.

Learn about Chat settings and figure out how customizations can make Chat work for you.

Gain insight into your agents' chat activities by building reports about Chat sessions.
title: Set Up More Features for Salesforce Chat
